The release also includes a brand-new studio track and video entitled, “Prayer of a Child. ”Filmed and recorded at RD Studios in Park Royal, London, Eric’s band was Doyle Bramhall II, Nathan East, Sonny Emory, Tim Carmon, Sharon White and Katie Kissoon.
